C   PURPOSE:  DRIVER FOR OPERATIONS WHICH BOTH READ AND WRITE FILES
C             CAN USE A SELECTION DOC FILE OR XMIPP SELFILE
C             CAN OPEN AN INPUT DOC FILE WITH ALIGNMENT PARAMETERS
